<body>
  <h1>How to Delete Your Data</h1>
  <p>At Leafie, you have control over your personal data.</p>
  <p><strong>To delete your saved plant data:</strong></p>
  <p>Open the Leafie app, go to <em>Privacy Settings</em>, and press the <strong>“Clear Saved Plants”</strong> button.</p>
  <p>This action will remove your saved plants and related data from your account.</p>
  <p>If you need further assistance or want to request deletion of other types of data, please contact us at:</p>
  <p><strong>Email:</strong> Leafie.helpdesk@outlook.com</p>
